Text: Why is the spoken and texted languages English, yet the torrent description is not?

Because, the OP is Swedish.  An English translation (courtesy of Google translate):

"Wikileaks - the leak as a weapon.
English version.

Wikileaks challenge the generals, bankers and politicians. But the attacks have only just begun. Behind the history of the world's largest leaks are a radical ideology. Meet the activists who are possessed of unlimited freedom on the web.

Ripped and uploaded by 15 Foot distro."
